# Agenda-v2

Agenda is a simple API allowing consumers to schedule meeting on-line. And this is version 2.

# Group User

Resource operations related to a user in the API.

## User Collection [/user]

### Log-in [GET /user/login/{?username,password}]

+ Parameters
    - username : `root` (string, required) - User Name
    - password : `pass` (required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "Key":"1e3576bt"
        }

### Register-user [POST /user/register]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "Username":"abc",
            "Password":"abc123",
            "Email":"abc@qq.com",
            "Telephone":"15000000000"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "Username":"abc",
            "Password":"abc123",
            "Email":"abc@qq.com",
            "Telephone":"15000000000"
        }

### Verify-key [GET /user/verify/{?key}]

+ Parameters
    - key : `1e3576bt` (string, required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "Success":true
        }

### Log-out [GET /user/logout/{?key}]

+ Parameters
    - key : `1e3576bt` (string, required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "Success":true
        }

### Delete-user [GET /user/delete/{?key}]

+ Parameters
    - key : `1e3576bt` (string, required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "Success":true
        }

