# Group Meeting

Resource operations related to a meeting in the API.

## Meeting Collection [/meeting]

### Create-meeting [POST /meeting/create]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "Key":"1e3576bt",
            "Title":"meeting1",
            "Participants":["p1", "p2"],
            "Start":"2017-12-12 13:00:00",
            "End":"2017-12-12 14:00:00"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "Key":"1e3576bt",
            "Title":"meeting1",
            "Participants":["p1", "p2"],
            "Start":"2017-12-12 13:00:00",
            "End":"2017-12-12 14:00:00"
        }

### Modify-meeting [POST /meeting/modify]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "Key":"1e3576bt",
            "Titile":"meeting1",
            "Add":["p3", "p4"],
            "Delete":["p1", "p2"]
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "Add":true,
            "Delete":true
        }

### Cancel-meeting [GET /meeting/cancel/{?key,title}]

+ Parameters
    - key : `1e3576bt` (string, required)
    - title : `meeting1` (string, required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "Success":true
        }

### Quit-meeting [GET /meeting/quit/{?key,title}]

+ Parameters
    - key : `1e3576bt` (string, required)
    - title : `meeting1` (string, required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "Success":true
        }

